11 September 2015 Please note that the scheduled media briefing below has been postponed . Social Protection, Community and Human Development (SPCHD) Cluster chaired by Minister of Social Development, Bathabile Dlamini will hold a media briefing to give an update on progress and achievements on the implementation of its programme of action.The briefing will be held as follows:Date: Monday, 14 September 2015 Time: 10h00 Venue: GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Hatfield, Pretoria.NB: There will be a video link up to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street in Parliament, Cape Town RSVPs: Takalani Mukwevho Cell: 082 227 9308 Email: takalanim@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries:Legadima Leso Chief Director: Cluster Communications: Social Sector &amp; G &amp; A Cell: 083 378 9495 Email: legadima@gcis.gov.zaIssued by Government Communication and Information System